    public final class ModuleDescriptionsComboBox
extends ComboBox<ModuleDescription>
    Combobox which may show not only regular loaded modules but also unloaded modules. Use it instead of ModulesComboBox for configuration elements which may refer to unloaded modules.
    See Also:
    ModulesComboBox, Serialized Form
